OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1778249473
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 23 May to Sat 6 Jun
OL,6,FCompared to earlier in the month,
OL,7,Fpatterns which bring more settled
OL,8,Fweather are more likely to dominate
OL,9,Ftowards the end of May. Whilst further
OL,10,Frain and showers are possible at
OL,11,Ftimes, there is likely to be longer
OL,12,Fspells of fine and dry weather.
OL,13,FTemperatures are most likely to
OL,14,Frecover close to average, perhaps
OL,15,Fbecoming warm at times. Into June,
OL,16,Fmore mixed conditions are likely with
OL,17,Fspells of rain and showers, but also
OL,18,Fsome drier weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
